summary: A female follower/spouse who specializes in Archery and Shock
descriptionHtml:
(Requires Dawnguard)

As it turns out, Serana has a little-known twin sister named Sarena. Unlike her sister, Sarena is an accomplished archer, though she has been known to resort to shock spells when arrows run short. Rumor has it she is also looking for love.

She likes to hang out at The Bannered Mare in Whiterun.
author: dbbolton
